px\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15551\" src=\"https://datsolar.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/den-led-nang-luong-mat-troi-sokoyo-capsol-10w-h22012.png\" alt=\"den-led-nang-luong-mat-troi-sokoyo-capsol-10w-h22012\" width=\"700\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://datsolar.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/den-led-nang-luong-mat-troi-sokoyo-capsol-10w-h22012.png 700w, https://datsolar.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/den-led-nang-luong-mat-troi-sokoyo-capsol-10w-h22012-300x157.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16723\" src=\"https://datsolar.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/den-led-nang-luong-mat-troi-sokoyo-capsol-10w-1205.png\" alt=\"den-led-nang-luong-mat-troi-sokoyo-capsol-10w-1205\" width=\"700\" height=\"366\" srcset=\"https://datsolar.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/den-led-nang-luong-mat-troi-sokoyo-capsol-10w-1205.png 700w, https://datsolar.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/den-led-nang-luong-mat-troi-sokoyo-capsol-10w-1205-300x157.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15547\" src=\"https://datsolar.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/den-led-nang-luong-mat-troi-sokoyo-capsol-10w-h42012.png\" alt=\"den-led-nang-luong-mat-troi-sokoyo-capsol-10w-h42012\" width=\"700\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://datsolar.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/den-led-nang-luong-mat-tro